data.description: Check out this well maintained home in desirable Bel Aire neighborhood.  Conveniently located near K96 and shopping.  With just over 2300 sq. feet of living space you will have the room you need and space for entertaining. Speaking of entertaining you will love the backyard with a new deck and inground pool.  Pool has new liner and pool pump.  Step inside the new patio doors into the kitchen/dining area.  Kitchen features granite counters, 2 pantries new dishwasher and eating bar.  All appliances stay including the washer and dryer. Interior features include luxury LVP flooring through out home.  For those cold winter evenings you will love coming home to a warm fireplace in the living room and the family room.  Sellers have loved and maintained this home. Check it out...it could be yours by Christmas!
